  "body": "\r\n**What keywords did you search in Kubernetes issues before filing this one?** (If you have found any duplicates, you should instead reply there.):\r\n\r\nService. TolerateUnreadyEndpointsAnnotation.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Is this a BUG REPORT or FEATURE REQUEST?** (choose one): FEATURE REQUEST\r\n\r\nref: \r\n- https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/39363\r\n- https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/39207\r\n\r\nTolerateUnreadyEndpointsAnnotation, aka `service.alpha.kubernetes.io/tolerate-unready-endpoints` annotation key, provides useful mechanism to discover pods without relying on healthiness/readiness. This is very useful and heavily wanted for stateful apps.\r\n\r\nHowever, so far it is still alpha. What is the plan to make this beta?",
